<h2 class="western">5. Validation Performed</h2>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm">PHP syntax checks were run against
	plugin PHP files after major changes. 
	</p>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm">JavaScript syntax checks were run
	with <code>node --check</code>. 
	</p>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm">Frontend issues reported from
	Elementor screenshots were fixed iteratively. 
	</p>
	<li><p>WordPress CLI bootstrap could not be used because the server
	CLI PHP environment was missing the <code>mysqli</code> extension,
	but standalone PHP linting passed. 
	</p>
</ul>
<h2 class="western">6. Key Files Updated</h2>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm"><code>ws-team-showcase-widget.php</code>
	- plugin metadata, asset registration, CPT class loading, activation
	hooks. 
	</p>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm"><code>includes/class-ws-team-showcase-post-types.php</code>
	- Team Showcases CPT and ACF local fields. 
	</p>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm"><code>includes/widgets/class-ws-team-showcase-widget.php</code>
	- Elementor controls, data source selection, ACF normalization, grid
