	</p>
</ul>
<h2 class="western">7. Final Backend Usage Summary</h2>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm"><strong>Team Members:</strong>
	choose Manual Repeater or ACF Repeater source. 
	</p>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm"><strong>Grid Settings:</strong>
