	</p>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm"><strong>Style &gt; Typography:</strong>
	name and designation typography, text color. 
	</p>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm"><strong>Style &gt; Button Styling:</strong>
	CTA button colors and radius. 
	</p>
	<li><p><strong>Style &gt; Search Bar:</strong> search width, colors,
	icon size/color, padding, border, radius, and shadow. 
	</p>
</ul>
<h2 class="western">8. Conclusion</h2>
<p>The plugin was built and refined through AI-assisted development
with human-directed feedback. The final widget supports dynamic team
showcases through manual Elementor data or reusable ACF-backed Team
Showcase posts, with secure AJAX filtering, modal details, backend
style controls, responsive grid controls, and all requested bonus
features.</p>
